These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
House: victorian, gothic-revival, cottage
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, purple, brown
1. the person who likes purple is the gothic-revival house##1
2. the cottage house is between the person who likes brown and the gothic-revival house##2
3. the victorian house is on the right of the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| House      | gothic-revival | cottage | victorian |
| Color   | purple     | grey    | brown   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
City: london, paris, hannover
There 3 different types of food: watermelon, lime, grapes
1. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the person eating grapes is between the person eating watermelon and the person traveling to london##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| City   | london    | hannover        | paris |
| Food     | lime | grapes | watermelon         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, bellflower, sunflower
3 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg, canasta
1. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
2. the person who growspoppy is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person who growssunflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Flower   | bellflower | poppy     | sunflower |
| Game        | mah-jongg  | canasta | scrabble |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk, water
House: ranch-style, art-deco, modern
1. the person drinking 7up is the ranch-style house##1
2. the person drinking water is between the art-deco house and the ranch-style house##2
3. the modern house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Beverage   | milk  | water     | 7up |
| House           | art-deco | modern | ranch-style |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, daffodil, aconite
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, gospel, d&b
1. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
2. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the fan d&b##1
3. the fan metal is between the fan d&b and the fan gospel##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Flower   | daffodil | aconite     | sunflower |
| Music-Genre     | d&b    | metal | gospel    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, blood-red, fuchsia
House: craftsman, gothic-revival, wooden
1. the craftsman house is between the person who likes fuchsia and the person who likes coral##2
2. the person who likes coral is the gothic-revival house##1
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Color   | coral  | blood-red   | fuchsia        |
| House         | gothic-revival | craftsman | wooden |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
House: palace, tower, victorian
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, milk, cola
1. the victorian house is on the right of the palace house##1
2. the person drinking water is between the victorian house and the person drinking milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| House          | tower  | palace  | victorian |
| Beverage   | milk | water | cola     |

