.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, pop, metal
City: prague, venice, london
1. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the fan metal##1
2. the fan pop is between the person traveling to london and the fan reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Music-Genre         | metal | pop | reggae |
| City   | london     | prague    | venice |

