.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, colombian, american
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, bike, boat
1. the person driving the boat is between the colombian and the person driving the taxi##2
2. the american is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | colombian | indonesian      | american      |
| Transport       | bike  | boat | taxi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
