2. the gothic-revival house is between the cape-cod house and the craftsman house##2
3. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Color   | apricot | ebony   | green   |
| House         | craftsman | gothic-revival | cape-cod |

