.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-13::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, coach, musician
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, september, april
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the coach##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who's birthday is in january and the software-developer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |     3     |
| Job         | software-developer | coach  | musician       |
| Birthday   | september | april | january |

