.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, hiking, gardening
The people have 3 different jobs:  photographer, writer, musician
1. the photographer is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the writer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | chess | gardening | hiking |
| Job     | writer    | photographer    | musician |

