House: townhouse, gothic-revival, farmhouse
1. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the townhouse house is between the person who's sport is cricket and the farmhouse house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2   |   3    |
