.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-16::.
House: colonial, modern, palace
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, lavender, fuchsia
1. the person who likes blue is between the modern house and the palace house##2
2. the modern house is on the far left##1
3. the modern house is the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| House   | modern | colonial   | palace   |
| Color         | fuchsia  | blue | lavender |

