.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-17::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, december, september
3 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, bridge
1. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person playing backgammon and the person who's birthday is in december##2
2. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |      3      |
| Birthday   | december       | september | november |
| Game         | canasta | bridge | backgammon      |

