.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, corn, apricot
House: wooden, palace, cottage
1. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person eating corn##1
2. the person eating corn is between the person eating apricot and the palace house##2
3. the wooden house is on the right of the person eating apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Food      | apricot | corn   | blueberry |
| House   | cottage  | wooden | palace   |

 